column2: Your original .Renviron will be backed up and stored in your R HOME directory if needed.

Your API key has been stored in your .Renviron and can be accessed by Sys.getenv("CENSUS_API_KEY"). 
To use now, restart R or run `readRenviron("~/.Renviron")`
Getting data from the 2020 decennial Census

[36mNote: 2020 decennial Census data use differential privacy, a technique that
introduces errors into data to preserve respondent confidentiality.[39m
